UPDATE pm_work_items
            SET item_type = ?, parent_id = ?, project_id = ?, position = ?,
                title = ?, description = ?, status = ?, priority = ?, assignee_id = ?,
                story_points = ?, sprint_id = ?, version = ?,
                updated_at = ?, updated_by = ?
            WHERE id = ? AND deleted_at IS NULL
